    "page_number": 0,
    "bbox": [
      58.56,
      607.69,
      537.88,
      645.07
    ],
    "text": "Misty conditions can be expected at some places in Central and Sabaragamuwa provinces and in Anuradhapura, Kurunegala and Badulla districts during the early hours of the morning",
